items.title: Fiskars Classic Loop Rotary Cutter Purple 45mm Blade Safety Lock--new Medium
items.description: Designed to fit your hand comfortably, this rotary cutter makes cutting a wide variety of quilting materials relaxed and easy. A curved shape with loop handle provides a natural fit for your hand to improve comfort and control, and a versatile design provides excellent blade visibility for left- or right-handed users. It even includes a sliding button that extends the blade during use and retracts it for safe storage, so you can safely keep your cutter nearby when working on large projects. Details: 45 mm ...
